OL,3,CLabour government pledges to introduce
OL,4,CHillsborough Law
OL,6,FIn the first King's Speech under a
OL,7,FLabour government, the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fhas pledged to introduce a
OL,9,FHillsborough Law, "to help rebuild
OL,10,Ftrust and foster respect".
OL,12,FNinety-seven men, women and children
OL,13,Fdied as a result of a crush on the
OL,14,Fterraces at the FA Cup semi-final
OL,15,Fbetween Liverpool and Nottingham
OL,16,FForest at the Hillsborough Stadium in
OL,17,FSheffield on 15 April 1989.
