OL,3,CLabour government pledges to introduce
OL,4,CHillsborough Law
OL,6,FFollowing the inquests, which found
OL,7,Fthose who died were unlawfully killed,
OL,8,Fthe former Bishop of Liverpool, Bishop
OL,9,FJames Jones, chaired an independent
OL,10,Fpanel into the disaster.
OL,12,FIn November 2017, the bishop set out
OL,13,F25 recommendations to the government
OL,14,Fto prevent future injustices like
OL,15,FHillsborough.
OL,17,FThe Hillsborough law proposal would
OL,18,Fplace a legal duty of candour on
OL,19,Fpublic servants and authorities, and
OL,20,Fprovide legal aid for victims of
OL,21,Fdisasters or state-related deaths.
