OL,3,CLabour government pledges to introduce
OL,4,CHillsborough Law
OL,6,FSpeaking on behalf of the new
OL,7,Fgovernment at the State Opening of
OL,8,FParliament on Wednesday 17 July, King
OL,9,FCharles said: "My Government will take
OL,10,Fsteps to help rebuild trust and foster
OL,11,Frespect.
OL,13,F"Legislation will be brought forward
OL,14,Fto introduce a duty of candour for
OL,15,Fpublic servants."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
