OL,3,CLabour government pledges to introduce
OL,4,CHillsborough Law
OL,6,FThe legislation will "address the
OL,7,Funacceptable defensive culture
OL,8,Fprevalent across too much of the
OL,9,Fpublic sector", the Government said,
OL,10,Fnoting the experiences of the
OL,11,FHillsborough families and victims of
OL,12,Fthe infected blood scandal across
OL,13,Fdecades.
OL,15,FLabour said the legislation is "part
OL,16,Fof our wider efforts to create a
OL,17,Fpolitics of public service".
