OL,3,CLabour government pledges to introduce
OL,4,CHillsborough Law
OL,6,FAlongside the legislation, they also
OL,7,Fpledged to improve assistance for the
OL,8,Fbereaved and those core participants
OL,9,Fat inquests and public inquiries,
OL,10,Fincluding providing legal aid for
OL,11,Fvictims of disasters or state-related
OL,12,Fdeath.
OL,14,FDebbie Caine, campaign director of
OL,15,FHillsborough Law Now said: "Only those
OL,16,Fwho have endured a long and arduous
OL,17,Fbattle with the state for truth and
OL,18,Faccountability will realise the
OL,19,Fsignificance of this announcement.
OL,26,@wD@\OU
