OL,3,CLabour government pledges to introduce
OL,4,CHillsborough Law
OL,6,FThe apology was the police's official
OL,7,Fresponse to a report by the Right Rev
OL,8,FJames Jones, who set out 25
OL,9,Frecommendations in The Patronising
OL,10,FDisposition of Unaccountable Power,
OL,11,Fpublished in November 2017.
OL,13,FSix years after the former bishops
OL,14,Freview, the previous Conservative
OL,15,Fgovernment finally responded to the
OL,16,Fformer bishop's report.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
