OL,3,CLabour government pledges to introduce
OL,4,CHillsborough Law
OL,6,FInstead of introducing Hillsborough
OL,7,FLaw, the previous government signed up
OL,8,Fto a Hillsborough Charter, pledging to
OL,9,Fplace the public interest above its
OL,10,Fown reputation, claiming a
OL,11,F"Hillsborough Law" incorporating a
OL,12,Flegal duty of candour was not
OL,13,Fnecessary.
OL,15,FLawyer Pete Weatherby KC, who helped
OL,16,Fdraft the Bill, said: "I hope today
OL,17,Foffers some comfort to the thousands
OL,18,Fof people who over decades have been
OL,19,Fdenied justice, truth and
OL,20,Faccountability by the state that
OL,21,Fthings might soon change.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@RO]xD@WOU
