OL,3,CLabour government pledges to introduce
OL,4,CHillsborough Law
OL,6,F"It is because of the struggles of so
OL,7,Fmany that we stand on the brink of
OL,8,Fchanging the law and I pay tribute to
OL,9,Fall the thousands of campaigners who
OL,10,Fhave stood up to be counted."
OL,12,FSolicitor Elkan Abrahamson, who also
OL,13,Fhelped draft the Bill, said the new
OL,14,Flaw "should stop all those who in
OL,15,Fpublic office serve themselves rather
OL,16,Fthan the public" and thanked the Prime
OL,17,FMinister "for keeping to the
OL,18,Fcommitment he made to us".
