OL,3,CLabour government pledges to introduce
OL,4,CHillsborough Law
OL,6,FBut Margaret Aspinall, who lost her
OL,7,Fson James at Hillsborough, called for
OL,8,Fa meeting with the Prime Minister,
OL,9,Fsaying she was "rather shocked."
OL,11,FShe told ITV News: "All I heard about
OL,12,FHillsborough was a duty of candour -
OL,13,Fwell we already had the duty of
OL,14,Fcandour so we've got nothing there.
OL,15,FAbsolutely nothing. I wanted the
OL,16,FHillsborough Law in all its entirety."
